canonical:
  title: 與元朝馮子振待制
  author: 權漢功
  language: lzh
  text: 玉樹淸風滿九天紫皇香案一儒仙大平文物重興後圖畫凌烟尙少年
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 與元朝馮子振待制
  author: 權漢功
  language: lzh
  text: 玉樹淸風滿九天。紫皇香案一儒仙。大平文物重興後。圖畫凌烟尙少年。
korean:
  title: 여원조풍자진대제
  author: 권한공
  language: kor
  text: |-
    옥나무의 맑은 바람 구천에 가득한데
    자황의 향안 앞에 한 사람 유선이네
    태평 세상의 문물이 다시 일어난 뒤에
    능연각에 그려지니 아직 소년이었다
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0240_010_0820&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 능연각(凌烟閣) : '
    value: 당나라에서 능연각(凌烟閣)에다 공신(功臣)들의 초상을 그렸다.
english:
  title: To Yuan Dynasty Official Feng Zizhen
  author: Kwon Han-gong
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The jade tree's clear wind fills the nine heavens,
    Before the Purple Emperor's fragrant altar stands one Confucian sage.
    After the great peace and culture flourished anew,
    Painted in the Hall of Soaring Smoke—still youthful then.
  footnotes:
    - The Hall of Soaring Smoke (凌烟閣) refers to the famous hall in Tang Dynasty China where portraits of meritorious officials were displayed.
